This shortbow can cause an arrow to shatter in midair and unleash a devastating spray of magical shrapnel. You can say the weapon's command word to destroy 1 nonmagical arrow fired from this weapon and send splintering shards of arcane energy in a 15-foot cone originating from the arrow's location. 